snippet.title: DEFEATING MARTH | Marth.exe (Formerly FE SD: Rearmed)
snippet.description:
I replayed the game countless times, I'm stumped on what more can be achieved :(

See Luigikid's video for the other endings! - https://youtu.be/Sv3tbygERlA?si=93gIA9ZGPLRxJca2

This is what I could piece together:

Ending 1: Trapped forever
- Everything gets swallowed whole by the evil that Hardin's team thought was all Marth's doing

Ending 2: Defeat cutscene
- Hardin fails to defeat Marth and is bade to replace him as the new .exe

Ending 3: Corrupted Marth jumpscare
- Hardin is unable to flee from Marth and gets caught by his corruption
